00:48:59.440 --> 00:49:01.068
Forget the answers they give.

00:49:01.068 --> 00:49:03.412
I'm talking about the
questions they raise.

00:49:03.412 --> 00:49:07.176
They're only legitimized by
the Judea-Christian world view,

00:49:07.176 --> 00:49:11.016
and what is the one thing
the Bible gives to you and me

00:49:11.016 --> 00:49:12.456
that none else does?

00:49:12.456 --> 00:49:14.316
The Getha hints at it.

00:49:14.316 --> 00:49:16.839
The Muslims are repelled by it,

00:49:16.839 --> 00:49:20.071
but there is no one
else that provides this,

