was the leading Shiite
cleric which whom I had

00:49:28.826 --> 00:49:30.625
a three R public dialogue.

00:49:30.625 --> 00:49:32.984
Ended the dialogue with these words.

00:49:32.984 --> 00:49:37.365
He said, "Professor, I want
to say something to you.

00:49:37.365 --> 00:49:41.913
"It's time for us in Islam
to stop asking the question

00:49:41.913 --> 00:49:45.080
