the cross and shut my eyes

00:51:07.073 --> 00:51:09.187
and try to see the cruel nails,

00:51:09.187 --> 00:51:12.547
the crown of thorns, and
Jesus crucified for me,

00:51:12.547 --> 00:51:14.647
but even could I see him die,

00:51:14.647 --> 00:51:17.782
I would much see a little
part of that great love,

00:51:17.782 --> 00:51:21.865
which like a fire is always
burning in his heart.

00:51:24.937 --> 00:51:26.935
What happened to his hands?

00:51:26.935 --> 00:51:30.518
Is the answer to a
world that's so wounded,

00:51:31.719 --> 00:51:34.703
and you ultimately reach
a wounded civilization

00:51:34.703 --> 00:51:37.375
