and is the only answer
to our relativistic cart

00:52:18.235 --> 00:52:21.683
where he pulls in the
absoluteness of his love,

00:52:21.683 --> 00:52:23.587
and changes the hungers.

00:52:23.587 --> 00:52:25.974
It's the only hope for the world.

00:52:25.974 --> 00:52:29.483
That's what Conrad Adanar
said to Billy Graham

00:52:29.483 --> 00:52:31.207
after the second world war.

00:52:31.207 --> 00:52:35.483
Mr. Graham, outside of the
resurrection of Jesus Christ,

00:52:35.483 --> 00:52:39.175
I know of no other hope for mankind.

00:52:39.175 --> 00:52:42.667
We have that message,
let the world see it.

00:52:42.667 --> 00:52:45.263
Life for him, serve him.

00:52:45.263 --> 00:52:47.063
It's a beautiful message.

00:52:47.063 --> 00:52:49.447
If you're not walking
in lockstep with him,

00:52:49.447 --> 00:52:52.507
let this be the evening of repentance

00:52:52.507 --> 00:52:54.607
in turning your heart around.

00:52:54.607 --> 00:52:58.927
If you do know him, let your
light so shine before people

00:52:58.927 --> 00:53:02.695
that they will see your good
works, and glorify your father

00:53:02.695 --> 00:53:03.819
who is in heaven.

00:53:03.819 --> 00:53:05.903
It's been my real honor,

00:53:05.903 --> 00:53:07.583
and even through Rick is not here,

00:53:07.583 --> 00:53:09.787
I'll convey to him my
thanks for the privilege

00:53:09.787 --> 00:53:11.663
of being here at Saddleback.

00:53:11.663 --> 00:53:14.380
You folks have touched the world,

00:53:14.380 --> 00:53:17.139
and may your greatest years
still be ahead of you.

00:53:17.139 --> 00:53:18.967
May I close in prayer?

00:53:18.967 --> 00:53:21.217
(applause)

00:53:23.079 --> 00:53:27.487
Thank you, God bless you,
thank you so much, thank you.

00:53:27.487 --> 00:53:29.183
(applause)

00:53:29.183 --> 00:53:30.350
God bless you.

00:53:31.627 --> 00:53:34.223
Thank you so much, thank you.

00:53:34.223 --> 00:53:36.775
Thank you, God bless you.

00:53:36.775 --> 00:53:38.259
Thank you so much&gt;

00:53:38.259 --> 00:53:39.842
Please let me pray.

00:53:41.783 --> 00:53:42.998
Let me close in prayer.

00:53:42.998 --> 00:53:46.073
Thank you so much for your kind response.

00:53:46.073 --> 00:53:50.240
Eternal father strong to save,
we need you more than ever.

00:53:53.455 --> 00:53:56.230
We are a desperate people.

00:53:56.230 --> 00:53:59.813
Lord Jesus, apart from
you we have no hope.

00:54:01.341 --> 00:54:04.899
I pray for every man, woman,
and young person here.

00:54:04.899 --> 00:54:07.316
Tonight, today, this weekend.

00:54:10.226 --> 00:54:13.871
I pray that hearts will be touched,

00:54:13.871 --> 00:54:16.283
lives will be transformed.

00:54:16.283 --> 00:54:19.615
You have given your servant a unique honor

00:54:19.615 --> 00:54:22.032
of standing on this platform.

00:54:23.890 --> 00:54:27.223
I don't deserve it lord, I really don't,

00:54:28.239 --> 00:54:31.906
but you in your grace
pour mercy upon mercy.

00:54:32.783 --> 00:54:35.275
Thank you for Rick and his team.

00:54:35.275 --> 00:54:39.310
How you have used them,
and I earnestly pray

00:54:39.310 --> 00:54:42.854
their greatest decades
and years will be ahead.

00:54:42.854 --> 00:54:45.029
Lord we pray for our nation.

00:54:45.029 --> 00:54:47.279
We go to the poles shortly.

00:54:49.081 --> 00:54:52.634
Sovereign lord who changes
the hearts of kings,

00:54:52.634 --> 00:54:53.717
do your work.

00:54:56.249 --> 00:55:00.339
May this nation never
lose sight of its roots

00:55:00.339 --> 00:55:03.756
and ever walk towards that glorious call.

00:55:06.777 --> 00:55:10.944
For you have endowed us with
some beautiful privileges

00:55:12.102 --> 00:55:13.769
of life and liberty,

00:55:15.627 --> 00:55:19.544
and to pursue the joys
that you alone can give.

00:55:20.985 --> 00:55:24.938
This land of the free,
may we ever be that,

00:55:24.938 --> 00:55:27.893
and use our freedom to honor you.

00:55:27.893 --> 00:55:31.506
What greater return can
we give you for that gift?

00:55:31.506 --> 00:55:34.281
Let your benediction rest upon Saddleback

00:55:34.281 --> 00:55:36.368
and its work all over the world.

00:55:36.368 --> 00:55:37.451
Be with Rick.

00:55:38.744 --> 00:55:41.145
Grant him safety and anointing,

00:55:41.145 --> 00:55:45.566
and all that work alongside
him with his servants heart.

00:55:45.566 --> 00:55:49.733
We come before you tonight with
hearts filled with gratitude

00:55:51.209 --> 00:55:55.005
for enabling us to live
at a time such as this.

00:55:55.005 --> 00:55:57.677
In the name of our lord, and our redeemer,

00:55:57.677 --> 00:55:59.260
Jesus Christ, amen.

00:56:00.578 --> 00:56:01.797
God bless you.

00:56:01.797 --> 00:56:04.047
(applause)

